condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :B.3 of this Section II and Section III of this Schedule 2 | Description :In order to ensure the timely carryingout of the audits referred to in paragraph B.3 of this Section II, the Recipient shall: (a) not later than three (3) months afterthe Effective Date, appoint an internal auditor; and (b) not later than six (6) months after the Effective date, appoint anexternal auditor, all in accordance with the provisions of Section III of this Schedule 2. | Due Date :15-Jun-2015

Finance Agreement :Part B.1 of this Section II | Description :To facilitate the proper maintenance of its financial managementsystem referred to in Part B.1 of this Section II, the Recipient shall, not later than three (3) months after the Effective Date,upgrade its financial management system, in form and substance satisfactory to the Association. | Due Date :16-Mar-2015
Finance Agreement :Sch 2 Section I. A.3 | Description :Establish SAICs (Community Dev. support Units) in each urban district. | DueDate :30-Sep-2011
Finance Agreement :Sch 2 Section I. A.3 | Description :Reactivate CDQs (Community Development Committees) in each Projectneighborhood. | Due Date :31-Mar-2011
Finance Agreement :Sch 2 Section I. D | Description :Conclude services contract for selected water supply activities. | Due Date:31-Jan-2012
Finance Agreement :Sch 2 Section I.A | Description :Recruit Safeguards, Communication & M&E Specialists | Due Date :30-Nov-2011
Finance Agreement :Sch 2 Section II B.4 | Description :Recruit external auditor | Due Date :30-Nov-2010
Finance Agreement :Sch 2 Section II C | Description :Upgrade records management system. | Due Date :31-Mar-2011
Finance Agreement :Sch 2 Section III. E | Description :Conduct annual procurement audits | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Section III of this Schedule 2 | Description :The Recipient shall, not later than one (1) month after theEffective Date, finalize and adopt the Electricity Master Plan in form and substance satisfactory to the Association. | Due Date:15-Jan-2015

Finance Agreement :Section III of this Schedule 2 | Description :The Recipient shall, not later than one (1) month after theEffective Date, update its accounting and financial management manual, in form and substance satisfactory to the Association. | DueDate :15-Jan-2015

Finance Agreement :Section III of this Schedule 2 | Description :The Recipient shall, not later than three (3) months after theEffective Date, appoint in accordance with the provisions of Section III of this Schedule 2, and thereafter maintain at all timesduring the implementation of the Project; a procurement assistant. | Due Date :16-Mar-2015

Finance Agreement :Section III of this Schedule 2 | Description :The Recipient shall, not later than three (3) months after theEffective Date, revise said Governance and Anti-corruption Plan in form and substance satisfactory to the Association. | Due Date:16-Mar-2015
